---
title: Creamy Mushroom Pork Chops with Crispy Potatoes and Brussels Sprouts
description: Pork chops blanketed in a creamy mushroom sauce is a recipe that’s an oldie and a goodie. The combo of savory mushrooms, rich dairy, and lean pork is enduring and familiar, yet it never fails to remind you of how good it is every time. On the side, oven-roasted potatoes and Brussels sprouts complete this comfortingly classic meal.
